<a href="http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=COM:2013:0036:FIN:EN:PDF" target="_self">http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=COM:2013:0036:FIN:...</a></p><p>EC, ‘Consultation by the European Commission on the Green Paper on unfair trading practices in the business-to-business food and non-food supply chain in Europe’ - questionnaire</p><p>
